{"tid":194960,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣 ATM問題 求解答","createTime":"2017-04-10T10:30:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-12T07:08:19.000Z","uid":19834,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1ba8e3a838a83981e233a0a1579ab120da55ea90","tid":194960,"uid":19834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T10:30:03.000Z","msg":"匯豐學生提款卡去到禁唔禁到錢?<br />\n<br />\n已開通左海外提款 <br />\n<br />\n我張提款卡後面得EPS 同 銀聯既LOGO<br />\n<br />\n依家禁唔禁到錢?<br />\n<br />\n我都有張白金VISA 卡 連住個戶口 呢張又禁唔禁到錢?<br />\n<br />\n感謝"},{"pid":"3433dd1684f99bfb7768f569ec739ee9e1a98c38","tid":194960,"uid":25272,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T10:30:57.000Z","msg":"Yes"},{"pid":"7da02bc2345525d09f84d5cd4d76e92fa8e450ec","tid":194960,"uid":85762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T13:10:35.000Z","msg":"有銀聯去大部分7仔都禁到錢"},{"pid":"a437a3fd5d51dcf40243ce7cac05ea3e88c49a98","tid":194960,"uid":77251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T13:19:23.000Z","msg":"用白金visa有機會變咗 信用卡透支現金提款<br />\n自己小心"},{"pid":"b55a74fe1fa362ede68faa73109a3695bdee70a0","tid":194960,"uid":77251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T13:19:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用白金visa有機會變咗 信用卡透支現金提款<br />\n自己小心</blockquote><br />\n基本上用匯豐嗰張已經冇問題"},{"pid":"b60149459a25ca6d61d102dacf8bf144ea7cfc83","tid":194960,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T16:08:48.000Z","msg":"帶定d現金去最穩陣, 萬一食卡, 壞機就大鑊"},{"pid":"5b3aa24015f613630cfdcba6b02e4a91c8a948df","tid":194960,"uid":7267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T16:16:20.000Z","msg":"㩒到 familymart 有提款機可以㩒"},{"pid":"ef272083d49c659111d23f0c76440a349a5b83fc","tid":194960,"uid":47080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T16:27:46.000Z","msg":"最好帶少少台幣出機場，因為機場好多ATM都襟唔到錢，尤其係台灣銀行有幾個A/C你㨂，如果張卡連咗幾個戶口，咁你一定攞唔到錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f82afe16035c7b41bf63648625d61107fa6055fa","tid":194960,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T17:34:46.000Z","msg":"年經<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n張咭有銀聯標誌，就揀有銀聯標誌既提款機。每次hkd15手續費（如果冇加到），每日提款上限ntd20000。"},{"pid":"23c0cc0f7cfc1122cb33fec156fb221fe2c93e78","tid":194960,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T17:41:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>匯豐學生提款卡去到禁唔禁到錢?<br />\n<br />\n已開通左海外提款 <br />\n<br />\n我張提款卡後面得EPS 同 銀聯既LOGO<br />\n<br />\n依家禁唔禁到錢?<br />\n<br />\n我都有張白金VISA 卡 連住個戶口 呢張又禁唔禁到錢?<br />\n<br />\n感謝</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nre你白金visa咭<br />\n<br />\n你張咭後面好似應該是有plus標誌<br />\n你揀既提款機要有plus logo<br />\n入密碼後<br />\n<strong>一定一定一定</strong><br />\n要揀儲蓄戶口先提款<br />\n<br />\nplus跟匯豐/恒生，每次手續費&ldquo;每次&ldquo;hkd25（如果冇加價），每日上限ntd20000<br />\n<br />\n如果揀左visa戶口都唔洗死既，貴些少，亦唔係會仆街既銀碼。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n補充返你問銀聯，我上面回覆：<br />\n手續費係每次提款收取<br />\n所以打算用幾多，最好一次過提。<br />\n分百九幾次提就收你百九幾次手續費了。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eabb8c8f21ba904bf4f4d38ed7ec6b20cc28c75","tid":194960,"uid":21035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T19:11:36.000Z","msg":"去台灣ATM㩒錢加埋手續費仲抵過香港找換店？<br />\n<br />\n點解個個都去到先㩒？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f6bc5b6b246935069b1b1b30629ccdb8ff80cc6","tid":194960,"uid":37097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T19:21:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去台灣ATM㩒錢加埋手續費仲抵過香港找換店？<br />\n<br />\n點解個個都去到先㩒？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇錯， 㩒機抵過唱定錢去"},{"pid":"8f1483b3d994d6c23daf1653aa38693636f41037","tid":194960,"uid":80110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T19:27:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去台灣ATM㩒錢加埋手續費仲抵過香港找換店？<br />\n<br />\n點解個個都去到先㩒？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上個月去台灣 去到上飛機嗰刻個銀包都係得嗰三百幾蚊港紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97883497c0dcce9fa960494c3b422c4e5f7c8dce","tid":194960,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T05:28:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>去台灣ATM㩒錢加埋手續費仲抵過香港找換店？<br />\n<br />\n點解個個都去到先㩒？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上個月去台灣 去到上飛機嗰刻個銀包都係得嗰三百幾蚊港紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n足夠啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d51110058cc509cc5b71709ae134edb99e6d86e","tid":194960,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T05:33:46.000Z","msg":"俾多一招：<br />\n<br />\n如果碌咭，簽單上有得揀臺幣及另一種貨幣（例如港元，美元都幾普遍），記得係揀臺幣。<br />\n<br />\n另一種貨幣，係商號幫襯果間銀行offer俾你嘅價格，通常都西到核爆。<br />\n<br />\n台灣碌咭都幾靚rate，記得還得到先好碌。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"373f10512ed7b78a82d91ac2a1bf3d74b28c5e44","tid":194960,"uid":44025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T07:08:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去台灣ATM㩒錢加埋手續費仲抵過香港找換店？<br />\n<br />\n點解個個都去到先㩒？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係抵啲<br />\n找換店個rate係3.82-3.83<br />\n去到用銀聯撳個rate係3.93到<br />\n計埋手續費都仲有3.9"}]}